title: MONDAY 3/22 - DeSean Jackson heads home
itunes:title: MONDAY 3/22 - DeSean Jackson heads home
description:
Wide Receiver DeSean Jackson , born and raised in Los Angeles, agrees to terms with the Rams. New Rams QB Matthew Stafford (0:50) talks about his expectations in Los Angeles. Kenny Golladay (1:26) joins the G-Men, while Sheldon Rankins (2:30) heads to Gang Green. Draft prospect Justin Fields (2:43) talks about his goals for his pro day, and Jaguars head coach Urban Meyer (3:29) gives us some insight in potential top overall pick Trevor Lawrence
